      "rationale": "Architecture search over 2, 3, and 4 hidden layers with 64, 128, and 256 neurons per layer was performed. The 3-layer 128-neuron configuration achieved the lowest validation loss without overfitting. Increasing to 4 layers or 256 neurons yielded less than 0.3% improvement in RMSE, confirming architectural convergence analogous to mesh convergence in CFD."
