      "rationale": "The neural network is trained to predict normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) directly. Post-processing converts NIH to RH relative to the predicate device. The quantities of interest are therefore directly aligned with the COU acceptance criterion (RH < 1), with no intermediate transformation introducing additional uncertainty."
