      "rationale": "A feedforward neural network with ReLU activations is appropriate for smooth regression over the hemolysis index response surface. The model form was selected following review of published ML surrogate literature for blood pump hemolysis prediction. Physical monotonicity checks (hemolysis increases with RPM at fixed flow) were confirmed to be reproduced by the surrogate across the operating envelope."
